name: HCPS(HenricoCountyPublicSchools)Calendar
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: h. c. p. s. calendar
des:
You can ask this skill "When is spring break" or "When is winter break" or "When is next holiday".
Skill will only show the dates which are in future. For e.g. when you ask "When is next holiday" it will look for holiday dates after current date.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
